Kubikwa ukuthi indodana kaNene, uSiyabonga, yathola imali engaphezulu kukaR25 million ‘ngokwazisa’ iPIC ngethuba lokutshala imali kule nkampani yaseMozambique okuthiwa ayikaqali ukusebenza. Ngaleso sikhathi uNene wayesayiPhini likaNgqongqoshe wezeziMali futhi engusihlalo webhodi lePIC. URamaphosa uthe uNene ucele ukukhululwa kulesi sikhundla ngoba ebona ukufakaza kwakhe kwiKhomishini ephenya ngokulawulwa koMbuso yidlanzana kungabeki isithombe esihle ngaye esikhundleni sobuNgqongqoshe. Ugcizelelile ukuthi ngokomthetho alikho icala alenzile uNene. 